title: Iron kitchenware production equipment (press) US-YD32-200
title_uz: Temir oshxona idishlari ishlab chiqarish uskunasi (press) US-YD32-200
title_ru: Оборудование для производства железной посуды (пресс) US-YD32-200
short_description: Every kitchen has metal kitchen utensils and they are always used. This pressing equipment of the US-YD32-200 model serves to produce exactly such containers. As the name of the equipment suggests, the press has a pressure of 200 tons. The pressing speed of the press is 5-12 mm per second. The motor power is 15 kW, and the weight of the equipment is 9000 kg.
short_description_uz: Har bir xonadon oshxonasida albatta metalldan ishlangan oshxona idishlari bor va ulardan har doim foydalaniladi. Ushbu US-YD32-200 modelidagi presslash uskunasi aynan shu kabi idishlarni ishlab chiqarishga xizmat qiladi. Uskuna nomidan ko'rinib turgandek press 200 tonna bosim kuchiga ega. Pressning bosish tezligi esa sekundiga 5-12 mm. Motor quvvati 15 kW, uskuna vazni esa 9000 kg ni tashkil etadi.
